ALMA-LINK
INTRODUCTION:-
->Social platform to enhance the career path of freshers    with the help of notable aluminies.
->Just like a child takes his/her baby steps with the help of parents we at alma-link try to nurture the career of the students.
->To be precise we are here for the IIT-fication of every university and small colleges to provide the necessary exposure  to every students.
WHY ALMA-LINK?
->We become the torch to find the lost talents and ideas once the student graduates.
->To be a part of the biggest student-Alumini community of ODISHA.
->Connecting budding freshers with notable Aluminies.
->Creating  a student base and providing a ocean of opportunities to the aspiring students.
IIT VS AMAR-COLLEGE:-
->The IIT is a brand that is unmatched in our country.
->The exposure and the huge student base is the difference between IIT and any other college.
->In 2022 9,00,000 students appeared for JEE-MAIN and there is only 16,000 seats in IIT.What about the rest students?
->We at ALMA-LINK are trying to make a genuine attempt to provide the exposure and alumini guidance that an IITian gets.
->Our motto is simple----->>>>"IITfication of every college".
PROBLEM-STATEMENT:-
->Lack of Alumini tracking and poor interaction between the alumini and the students presently studying.
->Every college has a variety of students with myriads of talents and ideas.
->each student has a story to tell.
->when the student pass out from the college the talent and ideas just vanishes in the thin air and the new students do not get the necessary exposure.
->So creating a community where there are all the necessary amenties to track the aluminies as well facilitate alumini interaction is our one and only goal......

WHY WOULD ANY STUDENT JOIN ALMA-LINK:-??
->Every student today want experience we at ALMA-LINK provide the necessary experience by facilitating alumini interaction.
->The student will have the chance to participate in different quizzes and puzzles that will be related to their domain. 
->Every student will get the necessary environment to foster their growth in this platform.
->Performing good in the quizzes can earn them recommendations and freelancing jobs.
->Provide an allround development of the student and also a chance to become a part of the biggest student-alumini community.
WHY SHOULD ANY ALUMINI JOIN ALMA-LINK:-??
->Every person want recognition and there is no better way to be recognised than fostering young student in their career.
->An alumini can also opt for creating paid courses and paid articles with minimal cost in our web-site.
->This community will boast huge student base and hence an alumini can also gain good amount new ideas from the students.
->Lastly the emotions of being able to help the young one will be of utmost pride for any person.
